high_descs: Turn left, walk through the hallway then hang a left, go to the bedroom and head towards the bed on your right.
Pick up the ladle from the bed.
Turn around and walk back to the hallway then hang a left and go the kitchen on your right and head towards the kitchen sink.
Put the ladle in the sink and rinse, then pick it back up.
Place the ladle on the left side of the sink next to the cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a ladle on the kitchen sink.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the bed.
Turn right to the bedroom and pick the ladle from the bed.
Turn left and turn right to the sink.
Put the ladle inside and rinse it well.
Pick the ladle back and place it at the top of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the ladle on the sink.

high_descs: Take the spatula in the bed
Put the spatula in the sink, clean it off
Place the spatula on the sink
anns.task_desc: Take the spatula in the table clean the spatula place the spatula on the sink
